# Global UI Rules

Any time UI code is written or modified, follow all rules, docs, and skills below **before writing a single line**.

---

## 1. Authority hierarchy

When sources conflict, priority is:
1. `.cursor/rules/` (always-apply rules — non-negotiable)
2. `docs/ui/` (design system specification)
3. `.cursor/skills/` (task-specific checklists)

---

## 2. Always-applied rules

Read and enforce **all four** rules files on every UI task:

| File | Covers |
|---|---|
| `.cursor/rules/ui-core.mdc` | CSS variables, spacing scale, touch targets, skeleton loaders |
| `.cursor/rules/react-ui.mdc` | Tailwind usage, component composition, `cn` utility, controlled inputs |
| `.cursor/rules/accessibility.mdc` | Focus styles, ARIA labels, WCAG AA, keyboard nav, reduced motion |
| `.cursor/rules/karpathy-guidelines.mdc` | Surgical changes, no speculative features, minimal footprint |

---

## 3. Design system docs — read before implementing

Read the relevant `docs/ui/` file **before** touching that concern.

| When you are about to… | Read first |
|---|---|
| Pick any color | `docs/ui/colors.md` — CSS vars only, never hex |
| Set any size / gap / padding | `docs/ui/spacing.md` — 4px scale only |
| Set any font size / weight | `docs/ui/typography.md` — Geist, max 2 weights, token names |
| Build a page or screen | `docs/ui/layout.md` + `docs/ui/responsive.md` |
| Add motion or transition | `docs/ui/motion.md` — functional motion only, no `transition: all` |
| Show empty / loading / error | `docs/ui/loading.md` |
| Add media (image, video) | `docs/ui/media.md` |
| Show icons | `docs/ui/icons.md` — Lucide only |
| Handle dark / light mode | `docs/ui/dark-mode.md` |
| Add any interactive element | `docs/ui/accessibility.md` |
| Unsure of visual direction | `docs/ui/philosophy.md` |

For components already documented, read the component spec first:

- `docs/ui/components/button.md`
- `docs/ui/components/input.md`
- `docs/ui/components/avatar.md`
- `docs/ui/components/badge.md`
- `docs/ui/components/modal.md`
- `docs/ui/components/toast.md`
- `docs/ui/components/post-card.md`

