## 5. Absolute constraints (never skip)

- **No hardcoded colors** — use `bg-*`, `text-*`, `border-*` token classes or `var(--*)` only.
- **No arbitrary spacing** — use the 4px scale; Tailwind classes like `p-4`, `gap-3`, not `p-[13px]`.
- **No `transition: all`** — always specify the property explicitly.
- **No mixed icon libraries** — Lucide React only.
- **No inline styles** unless the value is truly dynamic (e.g. computed width from JS).
- **Dark mode is primary** — design dark first, verify light second.
- **Touch target ≥ 44×44 px** on all interactive elements.
- **Reuse before creating** — check `apps/web/components/shared/` and `apps/web/modules/*/components/` before writing a new component.
